itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"咪係"},{"pid":"8bc9586b0df6e91071ab45ea21a85aa5d989e6dd","tid":1834819,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T00:19:40.000Z","msg":"返咁多份工<br />\n個個老細都十級爛口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e55830251b88c04de5c9771ade8e48b5c80c5a","tid":1834819,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T00:22:34.000Z","msg":"0.01分拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵十幾廿萬一個月既鬼佬日日講粗口"},{"pid":"64fd2de050db1479ef9cf4aaf387bdd8f7d99505","tid":1834819,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"有時候粗口字先可以最貼切形容個情況喎<br />\n咁做會唔會好鳩呀vs咁做會唔會唔係太好呀<br />\n我一定揀前者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa8d59450963fcbf7dbf6c30b4e6fe2ca149384","tid":1834819,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"我老細唔講粗口<br />\n但係仆街陷家產一條<br />\n同政府講野一尻樣<br />\n剩係識哂官腔"},{"pid":"ff209e4e3528778d971345d07d98daf59b15031a","tid":1834819,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"咪戇尻啦⋯⋯<br />\n食死貓都唔屌柒佢...<br />\n上司仲情緒化過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}